“2020年东京奥运会将如期举行”。
"The 2020 Tokyo Olympic Games will be held on schedule.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 南博一当地时间21日，日本官房长官菅义伟表示，2020年东京奥运会和残奥会将如期举行。
Japanese Chief Cabinet Secretary Naoto Kan said Sunday that the 2020 Tokyo Olympic and Paralympic Games would be held as scheduled.
据日本共同社21日报道，菅义伟在21日的记者会上强调，2020年东京奥运会和残奥会将如期举行。
Japan's Kyodo news agency reported on the 21st, Kan stressed that the 2020 Tokyo Olympic and Paralympic Games will be held as scheduled.
他指出，日本政府将结合新冠肺炎扩散的情况，为举办对运动员和观众而言安心安全的大会，切实推进筹备工作。
He pointed out that the Japanese Government will take forward the preparations for a safe and secure conference for athletes and spectators in the light of the spread of pneumonia in the New Crown.
关于政府防止疫情扩散的应对措施，菅义伟则表示，国际奥委会相信日本正在妥善应对。
Regarding the government's response to the spread of the epidemic, Mr. Kan said the IOC believes Japan is responding appropriately.
据悉，东京奥运会计划今年7月24日开幕，8月9日闭幕，残奥会将在8月25日至9月6日间举行。
The Tokyo Olympics are scheduled to open on July 24 and close on August 9, and the Paralympic Games will be held between August 25 and September 6, the report said.
随着日本的新型冠状病毒感染人数不断攀升，有人担心东京奥运会受到疫情影响。
With the number of new coronavirus infections rising in Japan, there are concerns that the Tokyo Olympics may be affected by the outbreak.
截至当地时间21日上午9点，日本共有728例新冠肺炎确诊病例，其中，来自“钻石公主”号邮轮上的确诊病例为634例，这其中还包含2例死亡病例。
There were 728 confirmed cases of pneumonia in Japan, including 634 confirmed cases on board the MV Princess Diamond, including two deaths, at 9 a.m. local time.
本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
